# Crew Orchestration

Supervisor routes; one skill per subtask. Never edit across layers in one pass.

## Mandatory verification

After edits to `flow/` or `crews/`:
1. `python -m py_compile` on changed modules
2. Run relevant unit tests in `tests/`

## Routing

| Intent | Agents (order) |
|--------|----------------|
| Flow / HITL change | acquisition-flow → control-layer → verification |
| Research crew / YAML | m-and-a-research → proactive-guardian → verification |
| Tools / Serper | crew-tools → verification |
| Tier matrix change | control-layer → hitl-checkpoints → verification |
